At a glance

   We are global leader in building materials and solutions. With about
   75,000 employees in around 80 countries, we operate four businesses
   segments: Cement, Aggregates, Ready-Mix Concrete and Solutions &
   Products.

   Find out more

Building for Growth

   Our Strategy 2022 is based on four value drivers: Growth,
   Simplification & Performance, Financial Strength and Vision & People.
   It will help us to deliver resilient returns and attractive value to
   stakeholders.

   Discover "Building for Growth"

Contact us

   Headquartered in Switzerland, LafargeHolcim holds leading positions in
   all regions across the globe. Your local LafargeHolcim team will be
   happy to share information on products, sales and career opportunities
   with you.

