Our business segments


     *

Cement
       We provide the widest range of high quality cements on the market.
       Our cements meet the most challenging needs, from environmental
       performance to specialty cements.
       lh icons blue cement
     *

Aggregates
       Our aggregates – including our recycled products – provide raw
       materials for concrete, masonry, and asphalt, as well as base
       materials for buildings, roads and landfills.
       lh icons blue aggregates
     *

Ready-Mix Concrete
       Our specialty ready-mix concrete solutions are tailored to meet our
       customers’ unique project needs – from efficiency to design to
       performance – in every corner of the globe.
       lh icons blue truck 01
     *

Solutions & Products
       We listen to your specific needs and requirements to supply and
       develop together the best solution to match them, from precast to
       asphalt, mortar and advanced solutions.
       lh icons blue building bridges

