   Session

   Third-party cookies

   Cookies created by domains other than the one you are visiting
   directly, hence the name third-party. They are used for cross-site
   tracking, retargeting and ad-serving.
   Host Name Description
   Lifespan
   irs.tools.investis.com AWSELB

   Third party cookie

