   About LafargeHolcim

   LafargeHolcim is the global leader in building materials and solutions.
   We are active in four business segments: Cement, Aggregates, Ready-Mix
   Concrete and Solutions & Products. With leading positions in all
   regions of the world and a balanced portfolio between developing and
   mature markets, LafargeHolcim offers a broad range of high-quality
   building materials and solutions. LafargeHolcim experts solve the
   challenges that customers face around the world, whether they are
   building individual homes or major infrastructure projects. Demand for
   LafargeHolcim materials and solutions is driven by global population
   growth, urbanization, improved living standards and sustainable
   construction. Around 75,000 people work for the company in around 80
   countries.
